    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082620/extras/a6d85460daadb1bf467587e77fe86a70.avif?t=1721726222\" width=554 height=80 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082620/extras/d6ea9320b4fc5c9df003f7c870e3fef2.poster.avif?t=1721726222\" width=550 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082620/extras/d6ea9320b4fc5c9df003f7c870e3fef2.webm?t=1721726222\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082620/extras/d6ea9320b4fc5c9df003f7c870e3fef2.mp4?t=1721726222\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>先敌预判、见招拆招、锁定弱点、一击制胜！用智慧击败强敌！</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082620/extras/b68af34ce49e6184b47167c6d09f60e6.avif?t=1721726222\" width=554 height=80 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082620/extras/13bb44b93c2e69e832b8d5079fad3f1c.poster.avif?t=1721726222\" width=550 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082620/extras/13bb44b93c2e69e832b8d5079fad3f1c.webm?t=1721726222\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082620/extras/13bb44b93c2e69e832b8d5079fad3f1c.mp4?t=1721726222\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>搭配几十种兵刃、饰品和招式，定义属于你自己的战斗风格！</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082620/extras/b874af136600d5dde9dc0f5d12d9c18d.avif?t=1721726222\" width=554 height=80 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082620/extras/bc81888d2866da88a36942c12a631167.poster.avif?t=1721726222\" width=550 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082620/extras/bc81888d2866da88a36942c12a631167.webm?t=1721726222\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082620/extras/bc81888d2866da88a36942c12a631167.mp4?t=1721726222\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>这不是动作游戏，但它努力呈现让人血脉喷张的刺激打斗效果！</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082620/extras/acd25895a46396207b61f0fffbee8b31.avif?t=1721726222\" width=554 height=80 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082620/extras/fb2b61e6b6f48c7ea23619162a3ab7ae.poster.avif?t=1721726222\" width=550 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082620/extras/fb2b61e6b6f48c7ea23619162a3ab7ae.webm?t=1721726222\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082620/extras/fb2b61e6b6f48c7ea23619162a3ab7ae.mp4?t=1721726222\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>一大堆武林高手等你来战！每个人都拥有迥异的身世、独特的战斗方式，学习他们的弱点并最终击败他们，体验无与伦比的成就感！</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082620/extras/945886b3664bff71300136c6be9c853e.avif?t=1721726222\" width=554 height=80 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082620/extras/95c3353ad2942ce705a37edc07da80cb.poster.avif?t=1721726222\" width=550 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082620/extras/95c3353ad2942ce705a37edc07da80cb.webm?t=1721726222\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082620/extras/95c3353ad2942ce705a37edc07da80cb.mp4?t=1721726222\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>有人的地方就有江湖，挖掘每个人的故事，感受有血有肉的江湖！</strong>",
